sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RBACProxy as Kube-RBAC-Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GORCH as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Detector as Detector InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Generator as Generator InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Storage as PVC/Database
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>gRPC TLS1.2+

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Data Ingestion
    Client->>Router: HTTPS Request<br/>Auth: None
    Router->>TrustyAI: Forward to 443/TCP<br/>TLS Edge Termination
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store Data<br/>Filesystem/JDBC
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: ACK
    TrustyAI->>Prometheus: Expose Metrics<br/>/q/metrics
    TrustyAI-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: Guardrails Request Orchestration
    Client->>Router: POST /gateway<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    Router->>RBACProxy: Forward to 8432/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RBACProxy->>RBACProxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Validate Token
    RBACProxy->>GORCH: Forward to 8032/TCP<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+
    GORCH->>Detector: Detect Request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    Detector-->>GORCH: Detection Result
    GORCH->>Generator: Inference Request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS/gRPC mTLS
    Generator-->>GORCH: Inference Response
    GORCH->>OTLP: Export Traces/Metrics<br/>gRPC TLS1.2+
    GORCH-->>RBACProxy: Response
    RBACProxy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job Execution
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator
    participant LMESDriver as LMES Driver
    participant LMESJob as LMES Job Pod
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI->>LMESDriver: Start Driver Pod
    LMESDriver->>ModelReg: Download Model<br/>HTTPS Token/Creds
    ModelReg-->>LMESDriver: Model Artifacts
    LMESJob->>Generator: Evaluate Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS/gRPC mTLS
    Generator-->>LMESJob: Results
    LMESDriver->>K8sAPI: Create Results Secret<br/>Service Account Token

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 4: InferenceService Guardrails Injection
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceServices<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: InferenceService Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>Add Finalizer + Config
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ACK
    Note over Generator: InferenceService Modified<br/>Routes via Gateway
    Generator->>GORCH: Requests via Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    GORCH->>GORCH: Apply Guardrails
